Name: Floor Is Lava
About the game: Floor Is Lava, is a 2d platformer where you have to escape an erupting volcano. Game features: - Running - Jumping - Coins - Timer - Keys - Multiple types of blocks. My name is Paxton and I'm 10. I've been learning C# and have been making games for over a year and this is the second game I've decided to publish. Please enjoy :)
